Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:10.33,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}那个时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:14.09,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}戴着无法飞翔的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:18.05,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:21.55,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:25.93,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.06,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}也许一直在误解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:32.40,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}持有自信迎面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:42.61,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.74,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:54.63,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:57.80,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.59,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:03.72,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:06.18,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:10.27,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:12.81,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}会有梦想绽放
